    "description": {
      "zh": ".44马格南子弹是上世纪初多年复装、调试.44特种弹的成果，这枚.44马格南弹药装填了一枚Wilson Combat公司制造的220格令\"极限穿透者\"开尖减阻弹头，拥有较其他.44M弹药极高的穿深和穿甲后效。",
      "en": "The .44 Magnum cartridge was the result of years of tuned handloading of the .44 Special. In the early 20th century, experimenters loaded the .44 Special and other large-bore handgun cartridges with heavy bullets and higher than normal powder charges to achieve superior ballistics and better hunting performance. One of these hand-loaders was Elmer Keith, a prominent writer and outdoorsman of the 20th century."
    },
